---
title: Spiced Prawns & Cheesy Crouton Salad with Herby Mayo & Caramelised Onion
description: These Aussie-spiced prawns are a down-under delight that’ll have you coming back for more! Paired with a cheesy crouton
salad, sweet caramelised onions and a luscious herby mayo - who could compete with that combo?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
